//It was about how less steps can be taken by an elephant to reach his destination
he can walk 1,2,3,4 or 5 steps at a single time(Step)...so if the destination is 26 units away
he will walk 5 steps of 5 then a single step of 1...so least steps can be taken would be 6.




Solution:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int a;
    cin>>a;
    if(a % 5 == 0){
        cout<<a/5;
    }
    else{
        cout<<(a/5)+1;
    }
    return 0;
}
